public class AbstractCollectionUserData<DATA extends AbstractCollectionUserData<?>>

createDependings

public DATA createDependings()
                                                            throws matrix.util.MatrixException
Creates all depending administration objects for given this instance. Only the depending AbstractAdminData.properties could be created. Creates depending AbstractUserData.site and properties for AbstractUserData.cues, AbstractUserData.filters, AbstractUserData.queries, AbstractUserData.tables, AbstractUserData.tips, AbstractUserData.toolSets and AbstractUserData.views. Created depending parents.
